OL,7,FA teenager was found with more than
OL,8,F#700 worth of drugs and a 15-inch
OL,9,Fknife after he used an electric bike
OL,10,Fto try to escape from a street warden.
OL,12,FLogan Winter, 18, was initially
OL,13,Fstopped in city centre in October last
OL,14,Fyear as part of an operation tackling
OL,15,Fthe antisocial use of electric bikes,
OL,16,Fwhen he rode off without warning.
OL,18,FNightingale Court heard street warden
OL,19,FPaul Smith chased the defendant but
OL,20,Fwas assaulted as he tried to grab his
OL,21,Fcoat.
