OL,7,FHaving ditched the bike, Winter was
OL,8,Fdetained by a police officer as he ran
OL,9,Ftowards The Hayes.
OL,11,FThe defendant was found to be carrying
OL,12,Fa large Rambo-style knife. A further
OL,13,Fsearch revealed he was carrying a bag
OL,14,Fcontaining 71 small wraps of crack
OL,15,Fcocaine with a street value of #710,
OL,16,Fas well as three mobile phones.
OL,18,FMessages to Winter's upstream supplier
OL,19,Fwere found on one of the phones, along
OL,20,Fwith a photograph of someone holding a
OL,21,Flarge amount of cash.
