OL,7,FAfter being arrested, Winter admitted
OL,8,Fthe phones were his but denied the
OL,9,Fdrugs belonged to him.
OL,11,FWinter, of Chapel Wood, Pentwyn, later
OL,12,Fpleaded guilty to possession with
OL,13,Fintent to supply cocaine, possession
OL,14,Fof cocaine, assault by beating, and
OL,15,Fpossession of a knife.
OL,17,FThe heard he had previous convictions
OL,18,Ffor possession of an axe, possession
OL,19,Fof a knife, and attempted robbery.
