OL,7,FMr Comer said Winter was placed in
OL,8,Fcare aged 13 and turned to dealing
OL,9,Fcrack cocaine to fund his nitrous
OL,10,Foxide addiction.
OL,12,FDuring sentencing, Recorder David
OL,13,FElias KC said: "You were making
OL,14,Fsignificant amounts of money from the
OL,15,Fsale of this drug. The court accepts
OL,16,Fyou were dealing primarily to find
OL,17,Fyour own addiction to nitrous oxide."
